column5: Because of change in schedule we have opening for 1 fisherman on a walleye and pike flyin trip- area is in off the clova road and north of 0-sullivan lake posted on here many times. we have fished here last 8 years with great success-total cost is about 700 US- we leave from eastern PA 7/14 return 7/22. good group - no problems - just good fihing-
